des: LagosJump Radio UK operating out of the West Midlands & Warwickshire is your gateway to Afrobeats and urban vibes, 24/7. Immerse yourself in the pulse of Lagos, from timeless classics to the freshest hits. Download our app to carry the rhythm with you, wherever you go. Let's make you jump to our beat!
